 <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;6:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-keys-links-to-terms.dita">The <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;6:25" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-keys-links-to-terms.dita">keyref</xmlatt> attribute enables authors to specify that references to
